## Common Workflows

### New Character Setup
1. Create base [[templates/character/character_sheet|Character Sheet]]
2. Add [[templates/character/combat_character_sheet|Combat Sheet]]
3. Set up relevant specialty trackers:
   * Combat: [[templates/combat/combat_technique_tracker|Combat Technique Tracker]]
   * Social: [[templates/social/social_identity_tracker|Social Identity Tracker]]
   * Spiritual: [[templates/spiritual/spiritual_practice_tracker|Spiritual Practice Tracker]]

### Quest Management
1. Create quest in [[templates/quests/quest_tracker_template|Quest Tracker]]
2. Link relevant NPCs in [[templates/social/social_relationship_tracker|Social Relationship Tracker]]
3. Prepare needed encounter templates
4. Track progress and updates

### Travel Planning
1. Fill [[templates/activities/travel_template|Travel Template]]
2. Prepare potential encounters
3. Track resources and supplies
4. Note discoveries and events

